Messages.Text:
Current date: Friday, 09 February 2024

Respond with a JSON object with ONLY the following keys. For each key, infer a value from USER_DATA:

{
  "explicitly-annotated": /* The City of type string */,
  "labelled-field": /* The Metal band of type string */,
  "inferred-from-nearby-text": /* The Hairstyle of type string */,
  "shoe-size": /* The shoe-size of type string */,
  "philosophy": /* The philosophy of type string */
}


Do not explain how the values were determined.
For fields without any corresponding information in USER_DATA, use the value null.

USER_DATA: 
            Hairstyle: Tonsure
            Metal band: Sad Iron
            Philosophy: Nihilism
            City: Cairns
            Shoe size: 55
